tak berlaku di sini.

520
00:37:30,780 --> 00:37:32,000
Silakan duduk kembali.

521
00:37:35,940 --> 00:37:37,240
Tolong tunjukkan di layar.

522
00:37:42,140 --> 00:37:43,280
Saksi.

