602
00:41:50,860 --> 00:41:52,040
Benar.

603
00:41:52,380 --> 00:41:54,396
Mereka berkolaborasi hanya
demi keuntungan pribadi.

604
00:41:54,420 --> 00:41:56,240
Mana mungkin peduli kesetiaan.

605
00:42:19,140 --> 00:42:22,000
