00:42:31,380 --> 00:42:32,520
Benarkah?

611
00:42:36,100 --> 00:42:37,320
Salinan?

612
00:42:37,580 --> 00:42:40,480
Kau bilang diikuti di rumah abu.

613
00:42:40,740 --> 00:42:43,676
Artinya mereka tahu
kau memiliki...

